Introduction

WayV-TEN&YANGYANG (Korean: WayV-텐&양양; Japanese: ウェイV-テン＆ヤンヤン) is the second duo unit of WAYV, a sub-unit of the boy group NCT. They made their official debut on August 17, 2021 with the digital single 'Low Low.'
